Package: NeStage
Type: Package
Title: Estimation of Ny/N, Ne/N, and Stage-Based Genetic Metrics
Version: 0.6.0
Authors@R: person("Raymond L.", "Tremblay Lalande", email = "youremail@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides tools to compute Ny/N, Ne/N, generation time, and 
    related demographic-genetic metrics from stage-structured projection 
    matrices. Implements the Yonezawa-based workflow used in population 
    genetics and plant demography, including exact (observed and expected) 
    matrix estimators and a sex-only transformation. Includes helper 
    functions for comparisons, reproducible logging, and minimal plotting.
